name: Freia Lobo
body:
### About Me

![Photo of Freia Lobo](https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/696163204456644608/cPbLSDGC.jpg)

I’m originally from Mumbai in India, and now live in New York City. I’m a senior at NYU studying Economics and Computer Science. Earlier this year I was named one of [NYU's Up and Comers](http://www.nyunews.com/2016/03/10/freia-lobo/). I help lead [Tech@NYU](http://techatnyu.org). I have interned at YouTube as a product manager, Google Shopping Express as a software engineer and Girls Who Code as a Teaching Assistant. I love [dosas](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dosa), coffee and cities. I read a lot of [books](http://freialobo.tumblr.com)
